title: 2009 May Grand Sumo Tournament (Summer Natsu Basho Tokyo) Day 1

2009 May Grand Sumo Tournament (Summer Natsu Basho Tokyo) Day 1 Top Division Highlights (with Japanese Audio)

I missed the first day so unfortunately I won't be posting the full day1 broadcast.
In terms of quality, I did quite a bit of work getting this to look good (Original video transmission is similar to SciFi-Sumo uploads). I think NHK is bouncing their feeds off sputnik before broadcasting overseas because the quality was absolutely horrible and their NTSC>PAL conversion equipment is pretty awful too.

Expect Day 2 Full English Audio Broadcast within the next 2-3 days. Video will be around 1.3GB per Day
